OL,3,CCrews tackle large fire in Greater
OL,4,CManchester
OL,6,FFire crews are tackling a large blaze
OL,7,Fat a building in Bury, Greater
OL,8,FManchester.
OL,10,FEight fire engines and three
OL,11,Fspecialist appliances were called to
OL,12,FMilltown Street, Radcliffe at 7:15pm
OL,13,Fon Tuesday 21 April.
OL,15,FGreater Manchester Fire and Rescue
OL,16,FService (GMFRS) said: "Crews arrived
OL,17,Fquickly and are using jets and
OL,18,Fturntable ladders to extinguish the
OL,19,Ffire.
